title: Bye Paul-icia! Narc Suckerberg Goes To Washington 4.11.18
itunes:title: Bye Paul-icia! Narc Suckerberg Goes To Washington 4.11.18
description:
In episode 124, Jack & Miles are joined by writer & performer Billy Scafuri to discuss Mark Zuckerberg's testimony in front of congress, some more unstable comments from Trump about sneak attacks and possibly firing Mueller, Paul Ryan deciding not to run for re-election, Margaret Atwood blaming 9/11 on Star Wars, Robert Kraft meeting with Meek Mill, Tristan Thompson's shady behavior, Chuck Grassley announcing a bill to protect Mueller, & more.
